title: B-24: Target Nazi Europe
description:
B-24: Target Nazi Europe: The Victory Bombers (2007) 


Take to the skies as Allied forces use air power to change the course of World War II. As Hitler&#039;s armies swept through Europe, the Allies&#039; aerial strategy led to victories at Ploesti, site of Nazi oil reserves, and Panteleria, a small island off the African coast that proved critical to the war. Rarely seen archival footage from the U.S. military and captured enemies takes viewers into the B-24 cockpit and into the heat of battle.



Length:
60 minutes
